import React from 'react'
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'

import MyCarousel from '../../Conteudo/MyCarousel/MyCarousel'

const PaginaInicial = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <MyCarousel/>
            <Container fluid>
                <Row>
                    <Col>a</Col>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col>b</Col>
                    <Col>b</Col>
                    <Col>b</Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default PaginaInicial
